  "text": "Brand familiarity was not correlated with the independent variables but did correlate with the dependent variables. Thus, following [CITATION_1] , we included brand familiarity as a covariate in the subsequent analyses. We used a two-way analysis of covariance (ANCOVA), with price-ending (oddvs. round-ending) and consumption motive (utilitarian vs. hedonic) as predictors.",
